<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.3.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Material+Icons%7CMaterial+Icons+Outlined%7CMaterial+Icons+Two+Tone%7CMaterial+Icons+Round%7CMaterial+Icons+Sharp"
    />

    <title><%= title %></title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div
      class="min-w-screen min-h-screen bg-gray-900 flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-5"
    >
      <div
        class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 rounded-3xl shadow-xl w-full overflow-hidden"
        style="max-width: 1000px"
      >
        <div class="md:flex w-full">
          <div
            class="hidden md:flex w-1/2 bg-indigo-500 flex-nowrap content-center p-10"
          >
            <img src="images/main-logo.svg" alt="" srcset="" />
          </div>
          <div
            class="w-full md:w-1/2 py-10 px-5 md:px-10 flex-col justify-between"
          >
            <div class="text-center mb-10">
              <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-3 text-gray-900">로그인</h1>
              <p>사전등록 때 입력하신 정보를 입력해주세요</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex -mx-3">
              <div class="w-full px-3 mb-4">
                <label for="" class="text-xs font-semibold px-1">이메일</label>
                <div class="flex">
                  <div
                    class="w-10 z-10 pl-1 text-center pointer-events-none flex items-center justify-center"
                  >
                    <span class="material-icons-outlined text-gray-400">
                      email
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <input
                    type="email"
                    name="email"
                    class="w-full -ml-10 pl-10 pr-3 py-2 rounded-lg border-2 border-gray-200 outline-none focus:border-indigo-500 required:border-red-500"
                    placeholder="gildong@email.com"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex -mx-3">
              <div class="w-full px-3 my-4">
                <label for="" class="text-xs font-semibold px-1"
                  >비밀번호</label
                >
                <div class="flex">
                  <div
                    class="w-10 z-10 pl-1 text-center pointer-events-none flex items-center justify-center"
                  >
                    <span class="material-icons-outlined text-gray-400">
                      lock
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <input
                    type="password"
                    name="password"
                    class="w-full -ml-10 pl-10 pr-3 py-2 rounded-lg border-2 border-gray-200 outline-none focus:border-indigo-500 required:border-red-500"
                    placeholder="************"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex -mx-3 flex-col text-center">
              <div class="w-full px-3 mt-8 mb-4">
                <button
                  id="submitBtn"
                  class="block w-full max-w-xs mx-auto bg-indigo-500 hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:bg-indigo-700 text-white rounded-lg px-3 py-3 font-semibold"
                >
                  입장하기
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
  <script src="js/login.js"></script>
</html>
